<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-06-0744 </DOCNO><TEXT>The duty of care must be recognised by the landfill operator which includesthe need to control landfill gas. The gas must be abstracted from thesite to ensure that there is no environmental impact through migrationor through smell. Suitable methods are discussed. Only when this potentialhazard has been harnessed fully, can this valuable energy source be usedcommercially. The options available are reviewed as well as means ofcleaning up the gas to make it more widely usable.</TEXT></DOC>